---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="分类已迁移">
  <section class="shell moved">
    <p class="eyebrow">MOVED</p>
    <h1>分类索引已经搬到新地址。</h1>
    <p>旧的课程入口还保留着，但新的分类页会更适合日常记录、研究札记、学习笔记和项目实践混在一起生长。</p>
    <a class="button-link" href="/categories">前往分类索引</a>
  </section>
  <script is:inline>
    window.location.replace('/categories');
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .moved { min-height: 62vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding-block: 80px; }
  h1 { max-width: 720px; margin: 0; font: 650 clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.6rem)/1.1 ui-serif, Georgia, "Noto Serif SC", serif; }
  p:not(.eyebrow) { max-width: 640px; color: var(--muted); }
  .button-link { width: max-content; margin-top: 18px; }
</style>
